This project incorporates components from:

1. HaGRID Dataset (Hand Gesture Recognition Image Dataset)
   - Used for gesture recognition models
   - Licensed under Apache License 2.0
   - https://github.com/hukenovs/hagrid

2. OpenCV (Open Source Computer Vision Library)
   - Used for computer vision operations
   - Licensed under Apache License 2.0
   - https://opencv.org/

3. OC-SORT (Observation-Centric SORT)
   - Used for hand tracking
   - Licensed under MIT License
   - https://github.com/noahcao/OC_SORT
